temperatures in the low 20\'s and a recent light fluffy  snowfall  at  higher
elevations. I continued on foot up the rough eroded  trail  another  long  2
miles to where it breaks out into open meadows for another mile traverse  to
the pass above Anderson Lake.  Here the snow was several inches deep over  a
