cover the front half of the boot) for the icy descent  down  the  trail.   I
reached the TH 2 hours later for the frigid blast down  to  the  car  on  my
bike.  15 miles, 4400 ft, 10:45 hrs, - Fay Pullen, Kent, 11/4.
