switchback, then followed the road to its end at the Evergreen Mtn TH.  An
attractive open ridge led steeply up past a minor wooded bump to the main
corniced summit ridge and the lookout (4300 ft 4:15 hrs).

     No views were in evidence as I was now in dense fog, nor could I find
