were not holding well.  So, not wanting to go sliding off into oblivion, I
postholed knee deep down the steepest section of the ridge until the angle
slacked off.  I made it back to the car without further mishap. 9 miles,

4350 ft, 6.5 hr, - Fay Pullen, Kent, 4/7.
