car.

While none of these peaks has the "required" 400 feet  of  prominence,  they
are all named, (though I am not sure why - the  history  of  that  would  be
interesting) and they make for a satisfying fall trip.

Total: 7 miles, 4250 ft and 9:15 hrs

Fay Pullen
