Iron Cr Butte (4280+ ft - 560P - Greenhorn Buttes Quad) - January 24, 2008

I had wanted to climb Iron Cr Butte when I did Greenhorn Buttes, but I  lost
so much time cutting the trees on the road I ran out of time. And, truth  be
