had another 500 feet of talus to go and I almost cried. I finally  staggered
into camp at 2:30 am (12  miles,  6600  ft,  18:30  hrs).  I  had  certainly
attained my goal of not spending another 12 hours in my sleeping bag  (which
was looking mighty good to me at that moment).

Day 3: Tuesday, October 6 - You can certainly understand why  I  didn\'t  get
