asked how much farther it was and seemed very disappointed when I told  them
they had a ways yet to go. They had no idea what a long  way  really  means!
(6.7 miles, 200 ft, 4:30 hrs)

Total: 25.4 miles and 9800 ft in 3 days

Fay Pullen



