road along the SW slope until I could access the W ridge. I had to  boot  up
the final 40 feet to the top.

I returned to the car in 1:45 hours  despite  several  miles  of  very  flat
road. The fact that snow that was in the sun was beginning to  ice  over  by
this time helped speed things up.

Total: 14 miles, 3800 ft and 8.5 hrs

Fay Pullen



