well, I had a great run back to the saddle where a spur not shown on my  map
led to within 50 feet of the summit of  Napoleon  with  the  sun  out  again
giving a reasonable view of Josephine. I had a nice  run  back  to  the  car
with even the level sections providing very enjoyable gliding.

Total: 17 miles, 3600 ft and 7:30 hrs

Fay Pullen

