 I took Davis Cr Rd, off Hwy 12 a few miles before Packwood, to FR 63  which
I was able to drive to 2600 ft before being stopped by  snow.  This  is  the
normal access to Purcell Mtn, a P2000 peak, but my goal today was Davis  Mtn
and Pk 4845 on the other side of Davis Cr. Logging spurs climb high on  both
these peaks and I thought they would provide good ski routes. They did.

