            'title' => 'Big Huckleberry Mtn (4200+ ft - P960) & Grassy Knoll (3680+ ft - P40) - Big Huckleberry Quad; and Augspurger Mtn (3667 ft - P1507), Hauk Butte (2880+ ft - P640) & Goat Pt (2361 ft - P241) - Willard Quad - April 26-27, 2013 
